Package: pifacedigitald
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-pifacedigitalio
Description: PiFace Digital daemon. XML-RPC server + easy event handle.
 PiFace Digital daemon allows:
 1. read/write IO ports with XML-RPC
 2. handle buttons events by executing files to /etc/pifacedigitald/event.d
